    {
      role: 'system',
      content: 'Return valid JSON only.'
    },
    {
      role: 'user',
      content: 'Repair this model output into valid JSON matching the required follow-up schema. Do not add new facts. Do not rewrite the content unless needed for valid JSON. Return JSON only. Required JSON types: summary, key_decisions, and risks_open_questions are arrays of strings; action_items, employee_faq, and ai_adoption_opportunities are arrays of objects; ai_ambassador_brief is an object. For action_items, each item must use exactly this shape: {"task":"...","owner":null or string,"deadline":null or string,"notes":""}. Keep JSON property names in English even when text values are Czech. Raw output: ' + $json.raw_model_output
    }
  ],
  temperature: 0.2
} }}
